    <bug_when>2013-06-24 05:36:37 -0400</bug_when>
    <thetext>Tycho support generating version qualifiers based on the revision in source control. This makes build versions reproducible and causes qualifiers to not change unless sources have changed avoiding unnecessary updates. Mylyn should enable support for this in the build.</thetext>
  </long_desc><long_desc isprivate="0" >
